{"tid":2383288,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"林建岳逆市擴充版圖做院線龍頭　宣布接手尖沙咀兩大戲院","createTime":"2021-01-27T21:17:22.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-28T00:00:04.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"46265d168aec7bec3d979a71049b5d10268b8365","tid":2383288,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T21:17:22.000Z","msg":"疫情下百業蕭條，去年戲院三度停開，至今仍未復業。逆市下林建岳旗下的洲立MCL院線（MCL）卻趁機收購K11 Musea及The ONE共18間放映廳於旗下，成為龍頭院線。<br />\n<br />\nMCL自新港戲院結業撤出尖沙咀後，昨日（26/1）MCL母公司豐德麗集團以5600萬元收購UA旗下K11 Musea的戲院K11 Art House，共有12間放映廳，並於今年3月1日開始接手營運。據悉，今次MCL以貼近市價約月租200萬接手K11項目。另外，今次是MCL首次擁有IMAX放映院。<br />\n<br />\n此外，MCL同時與The ONE商場簽約以低於現時市價的100萬月租，將於2023年接替目前經營的百老匯院線，共6間放映廳。屆時尖沙咀的4間戲院中，林建岳個人將獨佔兩間，放映院數目增至約73間。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210127/431226035153932288368047.jpeg/GB9UyuHCiq-sct07Q9CxegyEMhbuxgB18YKK3_GCit8?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210127%2F431226035153932288368047.jpeg%2FGB9UyuHCiq-sct07Q9CxegyEMhbuxgB18YKK3_GCit8%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=3cd47ff9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210108/424197263934361600403786.jpeg/s2vCQFg0o4zmUY74YOGA5CXNiZg0VTBtxuasK8bmrCs?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210108%2F424197263934361600403786.jpeg%2Fs2vCQFg0o4zmUY74YOGA5CXNiZg0VTBtxuasK8bmrCs%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=f1e4fe94&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b9ec655245c8b9eec8b9fedd5978939907808a73","tid":2383288,"uid":3241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T22:22:55.000Z","msg":"党需要你嘅時候日日播建党偉業都仲得"},{"pid":"95e442ccfa9c40304ddd1a4584089de7a7c2b193","tid":2383288,"uid":364767,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T22:30:26.000Z","msg":"（...今次MCL以貼近市價約月租200萬接手K11項目....）<br />\n林建岳的投資有邊次賺錢？<br />\n收埋富麗華搞到麗新破產咁滯"},{"pid":"a1b572733c89130c3d12d8f54625ccdeee75913f","tid":2383288,"u